@startuml 69_viewBlogDetail
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1
hide footbox

actor Farmer as "Users"
boundary BlogPage as UI 
control blogController as Controller 
participant ":blogService" as Service 
participant ":knowledgeBlogModel" as Model 
database Database as DB 


Farmer -> UI : 1. Users click on a specific blog
activate Farmer
activate UI
UI -> Controller : 2. Get blog detail request
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : 3. getKnowledgeBlogDetail(blogId)
activate Service
Service -> Model : 4. findById(blogId)
activate Model
Model -> DB : 5. Execute query
activate DB
DB --> Model : 6. Return result
deactivate DB
Model --> Service : 7. Return blog detail
deactivate Model
Service --> Controller : 8. Return blog detail
deactivate Service
Controller --> UI : 9. Show blog detail
deactivate Controller
UI --> Farmer : 10. Display blog detail
deactivate UI
deactivate Farmer
@enduml